<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ASCII"?>
<caldef:CalDefinitionFile xmlns:caldef="http://www.caltools.gm.com/caldef" Description="This caldef contains calibrations pertient to the GIS-657 (Global B Low Radio Component Diagnostic Specification) ">
  <CalDefFileVersion>5</CalDefFileVersion>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>1</Version>
    <Date>6/13/2016</Date>
    <Description>Inital release of this caldef file for GIS-657 (Global B Low Radio Component Diagnostic Specification) calibrations. </Description>
    <Author>Sarath Yyllapantul</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>2</Version>
    <Date>6/15/2017</Date>
    <Description>Updated the usage field for all of the calibration to support the new &quot;Global A/B&quot; categorization in the CalDef tool.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>3</Version>
    <Date>6/18/2017</Date>
    <Description>Within the GIS657_DiagnosticCalDef_GlobalB.caldef file added usage of GEM to all of the calibrations within this caldef file.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>4</Version>
    <Date>June 11th, 2018</Date>
    <Description>Made the following DTC enable mask calibration additions and deletions for CR#: 1699469 within the GIS657_DiagnosticCalDef_GlobalB.caldef file to reflect to the Low Radio DTC masks in the  latest 140 ODX file for Global B/GEM: Added the following 103 DTC enable mask calibrations: 1.) DTC_MASK_P0602_00, 2.) DTC_MASK_B1033_11, 3.) DTC_MASK_B1033_12, 4.) DTC_MASK_B1033_13, 5.) DTC_MASK_B1034_11, 6.) DTC_MASK_B1034_12, 7.) DTC_MASK_B1034_13, 8.) DTC_MASK_B1114_11, 9.) DTC_MASK_B1114_13, 10.) DTC_MASK_B1236_11, 11.) DTC_MASK_B1236_12, 12.)  DTC_MASK_B1236_13, 13.) DTC_MASK_B1274_11, 14.) DTC_MASK_B1274_12, 15.) DTC_MASK_B1274_13, 16.) DTC_MASK_B1274_25, 17.) DTC_MASK_B1274_28, 18.) DTC_MASK_B137B_11, 19.) DTC_MASK_B137B_12, 20.) DTC_MASK_B137B_13, 21.) DTC_MASK_B137B_25, 22.) DTC_MASK_B137B_28, 23.) DTC_MASK_B137C_11, 24.) DTC_MASK_B137C_12, 25.) DTC_MASK_B137C_13, 26.) DTC_MASK_B137C_25, 27.) DTC_MASK_B137C_28, 28.) DTC_MASK_B137D_11, 29.) DTC_MASK_B137D_12, 30.) DTC_MASK_B137D_13, 31.) DTC_MASK_B137D_25, 32.) DTC_MASK_B137D_28, 33.) DTC_MASK_B13A7_11, 34.) DTC_MASK_B13A7_13, 35.) DTC_MASK_B13AB_11, 36.) DTC_MASK_B13AB_13, 37.) DTC_MASK_B13ED_11, 38.) DTC_MASK_B13ED_13, 39.) DTC_MASK_B15AF_11, 40.) DTC_MASK_B15AF_13, 41.) DTC_MASK_B1737_11, 42.) DTC_MASK_B1737_13, 43.) DTC_MASK_B1960_11, 44.) DTC_MASK_B1960_12, 45.) DTC_MASK_B1960_13, 46.) DTC_MASK_B1961_11, 47.) DTC_MASK_B1961_12, 48.) DTC_MASK_B1961_13, 49.) DTC_MASK_B1962_11, 50.) DTC_MASK_B1962_12, 51.) DTC_MASK_B1962_13, 52.) DTC_MASK_B1963_11, 53.) DTC_MASK_B1963_12, 54.) DTC_MASK_B1963_13, 55.) DTC_MASK_B1964_00, 56.) DTC_MASK_B1965_00, 57.) DTC_MASK_B19B1_52, 58.) DTC_MASK_B1A36_11, 59.) DTC_MASK_B1A36_13, 60.) DTC_MASK_B1A62_4A, 61.) DTC_MASK_B1A62_82, 62.) DTC_MASK_B1A62_86, 63.) DTC_MASK_B1ABD_00, 64.) DTC_MASK_U0101_00, 65.) DTC_MASK_U0140_00, 66.) DTC_MASK_U0155_00, 67.) DTC_MASK_U0164_00, 68.) DTC_MASK_U0198_00_GlobalB, 69.) DTC_MASK_U020C_00, 70.) DTC_MASK_U0264_00, 71.) DTC_MASK_U1008_11, 72.) DTC_MASK_U1008_13, 73.) DTC_MASK_U1008_1B, 74.) DTC_MASK_U1008_29, 75.) DTC_MASK_U1611_00, 76.) DTC_MASK_U1818_00, 77.) DTC_MASK_U1967_00, 78.) DTC_MASK_U1967_81, 79.) DTC_MASK_U1967_84, 80.) DTC_MASK_U1967_85, 81.) DTC_MASK_U1967_89, 82.) DTC_MASK_U196E_00, 83.) DTC_MASK_U196E_84, 84.) DTC_MASK_U196E_85, 85.) DTC_MASK_U196E_89, 86.) DTC_MASK_U3000_41, 87.) DTC_MASK_U3000_42, 88.) DTC_MASK_U3000_43, 89.) DTC_MASK_U3000_44, 90.) DTC_MASK_U3000_45, 91.) DTC_MASK_U3000_46, 92.) DTC_MASK_U3000_47, 93.) DTC_MASK_U3000_48, 94.) DTC_MASK_U3000_49, 95.) DTC_MASK_U3000_4A, 96.) DTC_MASK_U3000_4B, 97.) DTC_MASK_U3000_51, 98.) DTC_MASK_U3000_52, 99.) DTC_MASK_U3000_53, 100.) DTC_MASK_U3000_54, 101.) DTC_MASK_U3000_55, 102.) DTC_MASK_U3000_56, and 103.) DTC_MASK_U3000_57. Also, deleted the following 4 DTC enable mask calibrations no longer required: 1.) DTC_MASK_U1962_00, 2.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_85, 3.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_89, and 4.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_84.</Description>
    <Author>Jeff Pawloski</Author>
